{"CATFALL":[{"def":"A rope used in hoisting the anchor to the cathead.","pos":""}],"CATFISH":[{"def":"A name given in the United States to various species of siluroid fishes; as, the yellow cat (Amiurus natalis); the bind cat (Gronias nigrilabrus); the mud cat (Pilodictic oilwaris), the stone cat (Noturus flavus); the sea cat (Arius felis), etc.","pos":""}]}